"ﾃｩ especificado, :c:func:`PyArg_ParseTuple` nﾃ｣o toca no conteﾃｺdo da(s) "
"variﾃ｡vel(eis) C correspondente(s)."

#: ../../c-api/arg.rst:403
msgid "``$``"
msgstr "``$``"

#: ../../c-api/arg.rst:404
msgid ""
":c:func:`PyArg_ParseTupleAndKeywords` only: Indicates that the remaining "
